Author: Adam Thompson <34922235+awthomp@users.noreply.github.com>
Date:   Wed Apr 21 18:07:41 2021 -0400

    Remove orphaned kalman filter code that supported cupy 7; run notebook for correctness (#354)

    Closes https://github.com/rapidsai/cusignal/issues/352
    Closes https://github.com/rapidsai/cusignal/issues/350
    Closes https://github.com/rapidsai/cusignal/issues/351

    We found a bug in the kalman filtering code where CuPy > 8.0 code was being treated like 7.0. Since we enforce 8.0 and above, we removed this orphaned code and reran our notebooks for correctness. I believe everything now works.

    Thanks to @apiszcz for the bug reports.

